      <abstract>
        <p>Jerry Lee, managing director at Health Medical Consumer Advertising and Marketing, is named president at TBWA/Health, new division of TBWA/Chiat/Day (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Jerry Lee, managing director at Health Medical Consumer Advertising and Marketing, New York, part of the Omnicom Group, was named president at TBWA/Health, New York, a new division of the TBWA/ Chiat/Day unit of TBWA Worldwide, also part of Omnicom, that is absorbing the employees and clients of Health Medical Consumer.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>Jerry Lee, managing director at Health Medical Consumer Advertising and Marketing, New York, part of the Omnicom Group, was named president at TBWA/Health, New York, a new division of the TBWA/ Chiat/Day unit of TBWA Worldwide, also part of Omnicom, that is absorbing the employees and clients of Health Medical Consumer.</p>
